CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 20, 1970, pg. 16, reads: "Hosts and Hostesses - Members of the teenage group of the Pittsburgh Chapter Tots and Teens, Inc., served as hosts and hostesses at the recent affair sponsored by the chapter at the Roosevelt Hotel.  From left to right: Alfred Hunt Jr., Donna Moncrief, Bruce Barnes, Diane Bolden, Dean Smith, Elizabeth Ward, and James Armstrong Jr."
TitMainTitle: Members of Tots and Teens, from left: Alfred Hunt Jr., Donna Moncrief, Bruce Barnes, Diane Bolden, Dean Smith, Elizabeth Ward, and James Armstrong Jr., posed in Roosevelt Hotel
